{
    "title": "A Morte do Vaqueiro",
    "artist": "Luiz Gonzaga",
    "composer": "Luiz Gonzaga / Nelson Barbalho",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ei, gado, oi\r</span>\n\r\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E... ei..ei..ei..ei...ei..ei\r</span>\n\r\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Numa tarde bem tristonha\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Gado muge sem parar\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Lamentando seu vaqueiro\r</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que não vem mais aboiar\r</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não vem mais      aboiar\r</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tão dolente a cantar\r</span>\n\r\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tengo, lengo, tengo, lengo\r</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tengo, lengo, tengo\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ei, gado, oi\r</span>\n\r\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Bom vaqueiro nordestino\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Morre sem deixar tostão\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu nome é esquecido\r</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nas quebradas do sertão\r</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nunca mais       ouvirão\r</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Seu cantar, meu irmão\r</span>\n\r\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tengo, lengo, tengo, lengo\r</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tengo, lengo, tengo\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ei, gado, oi\r</span>\n\r\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sacudido numa cova\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Desprezado do senhor\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Só lembrado do cachorro\r</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que inda chora a sua dor\r</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É demais,      tanta dor\r</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A chorar, com amor\r</span>\n\r\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tengo, lengo, tengo, lengo\r</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tengo, lengo, tengo\r</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ei, gado, oi\r</span>\n\r\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\r\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E... ei..ei..ei..ei...ei..ei</span>\n",
